### Price Tier Summary

- **Budget Tier (under $50):** Ikea Sniglar Crib ($79.99 - close to budget), Tommee Tippee Closer to Nature Bottle ($9.99), Luvs Ultra Leakguards ($34.99), Vtech DM221 Audio Monitor ($29.99), Infantino Flip 4-in-1 Carrier ($39.99), Evenflo Pivot Stroller ($169.99 - close), Evenflo SafeMax Car Seat ($149.99), Seventh Generation Wipes ($12.99), Kirkland Signature Formula ($22.99)
- **Mid-Range ($50-$200):** Dr. Brown's Bottles ($12.99-$25.99), Pampers/Huggies Diapers ($47.99-$49.99), HelloBaby Monitor ($69.99), Boba 4G Carrier ($129.99), Graco Modes Stroller ($199.99), Graco/Graco SnugRide ($249.99), Chicco Bravo Trio ($379.99), Babyganics Products
- **Premium (over $200):** Babyletto Hudson Crib ($349.99), DaVinci Kalani Crib ($279.99), Nanit Pro Monitor ($299.99), UPPAbaby Mesa Car Seat ($349.99), Britax Boulevard ($329.99), UPPAbaby Vista Stroller ($999.99), BOB Revolution Flex ($549.99)

